{"article_id":"iSzI8fJLCuANbVSh","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Marco Rubio 's uneven debate performance just days before Tuesday 's New Hampshire primary has emboldened a trio of governors","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"seeking to stem his rise in the Republican race for president .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"But","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"if Rubio 's rivals can slow him in New Hampshire ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"they are likely to leave the GOP with a muddled mix of establishment contenders and no clear favorite","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"to challenge Donald Trump and Ted Cruz .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"At the heart of the battle between Rubio and Chris Christie , John Kasich and Jeb Bush is whether the freshman Florida senator has the experience and policy depth","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"to serve as president","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"- or whether he 's simply a well-spoken lightweight .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"Christie unleashed withering attacks against Rubio in Saturday 's debate ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"and the New Jersey governor tripped up Rubio","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"by calling him out in real-time for his reliance on rehearsed talking points .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"The morning after , Christie declared","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"the Republican contest a changed race .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"`` There was a march amongst some in the chattering class","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"to anoint Sen. Rubio , ''","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"Christie said on CNN 's State of the Union .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"`` I think","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"after last night ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"that 's over . ''","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Christie and his fellow governors need that to be the case ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"given that they 've staked their White House hopes on New Hampshire .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Without a strong showing ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"each will face enormous pressure","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"to drop out from Republican Party leaders","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"eager to rally around a single candidate","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"who can challenge Cruz and Trump , the top-two finishers in the lead-off Iowa caucuses .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"Trump has held a commanding lead in New Hampshire preference polls for months .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"Cruz is in the mix with Rubio and the governors ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"though his campaign is more focused on the Southern states","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"that follow later in the primary calendar .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"The prospect","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"of Trump or Cruz winning the GOP nomination","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"has set many Republican leaders on edge ,","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"and that anxiousness is only likely to increase","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"should New Hampshire voters leave Rubio and the governors clustered together in the primary results ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"failing to anoint one as their preferred challenger to the front-runners .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"A Monmouth University survey","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"released Sunday ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"still shows Trump with a commanding double-digit lead over his Republican rivals ,","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"with 30 percent of likely Republican primary voters saying","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"they would vote for him .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"But there 's a cluster of candidates","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"statistically tied for second place :","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Kasich has 14 percent of would be voters ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Rubio came in with 13 percent ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"former Florida Gov . Jeb Bush also had 13 percent ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"and Cruz had 12 percent support .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"While most candidates remained unchanged in their polling numbers from last month 's Monmouth survey ,","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"Bush jumped nine points since January .","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"The Monmouth survey indicated","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"that just 9 percent of N.H. Republican voters are undecided .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"The poll was taken before Saturday 's debate ,","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"but no other Republican candidates had double digit support .","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"Rubio emerged from Iowa looking","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"as though he was that candidate ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"with a third-place finish in Iowa","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"that was stronger","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"than expected .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"Rival campaigns conceded privately in the days","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"leading up to the debate","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"that he was pulling away from the governors .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"But the Florida senator stumbled in Saturday 's debate","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"when challenged about his qualifications ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"repeatedly falling back on a retort","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"meant to distinguish himself from President Barack Obama ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"who also won the White House as a first-term senator .","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"For Barbara O'Brien , an undecided voter","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"who had been considering voting for Rubio ,","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"it was enough","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"to convince her","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"he was n't the right choice .","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"`` He kept saying the same thing over and over again , ''","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"said O'Brien , a 67-year-old from Manchester","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"who is one of New Hampshire 's many registered independents .","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"`` He did n't look presidential ''","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"GOP voter Judy McKenna , 66 , had been leaning toward Rubio ,","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"but said","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"she was `` disappointed '' in his debate performance .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"`` The governors all made great points about experience , especially Christie ,","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"and Rubio did not have any answer","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"to counter that argument , ''","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"McKenna said .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"Rubio acknowledged the criticism during a rally in Londonderry on Sunday morning .","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"He then proceeded to repeat the same line","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"that put him in Christie 's crosshairs .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"`` I 'm going to say it again , ''","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"he told the audience of more than 800","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"gathered in a school cafeteria .","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"`` The reason","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"why these things are troubling","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"is because Barack Obama is the first president , at least in my lifetime ,","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"that wants to change the country .","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"Change the country ,","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"not fix it . ''","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"Rubio senior adviser Todd Harris said","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"the candidate 's repetition underscores his laser focus","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"on upending the Obama administration 's agenda .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"`` We 're going to continue to attack Barack Obama 's record over and over and over again , ''","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"Harris said .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"there is any Republican primary voter","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"who was watching that debate","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"who was saying","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"I wish","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"he would lay off of Barack Obama . ''","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"Seeking to counter the notion of a misstep ,","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"Rubio 's campaign said","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"it raised $ 600,000 during the debate , three times more","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"than it has brought in during previous debates .","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"The fundraising numbers were unverifiable .","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"The senator 's crowds remained large and enthusiastic on Sunday ,","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"and some of the many undecided voters","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"who attended his events","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"said","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"they were more bothered by Christie 's aggressive demeanor .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"`` It was tiresome .","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"I 've heard it before , ''","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"said Katherine Bringhurst , a 66-year-old retired office manager .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"She 's undecided","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"heading into Tuesday 's election ,","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"but leaning toward Rubio .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"Maria Tourlitis , an independent from Hudson , decided to vote for Rubio","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"after hearing him speak in her hometown on Saturday .","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"As she greeted the senator after the event ,","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"she leaned in","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"and said :","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"`` At the next debate , please stand up to Christie . ''","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"If Christie 's aggressive attacks on Rubio result in his own standing tumbling ,","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"it could benefit Bush , the former governor of Florida , and Kasich , the current governor of Ohio .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"Both stepped back in the debate","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"to allow Christie to take the lead","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"in targeting Rubio ,","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"though they were happy to relish in the afterglow .","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"`` He 's a great speaker , ''","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"Bush said of Rubio , his one-time political protégé , on Fox News Sunday .","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"`` But he came across as totally scripted and kind of robotic . ''","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"Kasich has prided himself on avoiding direct criticism of his rivals during the campaign ,","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"and kept up that strategy both in the debate and as he campaigned Sunday .","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"`` Would n't it be great","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"if we could win being positive ? ''","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"Kasich said on Fox News .","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":143,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":144,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":145,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":146,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":147,"text":"Associated Press writer Sergio Bustos contributed to this report from Salem , New Hampshire .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":295,"left":289,"right":294,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":184,"right":288,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":156,"right":183,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":153,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":149,"right":152,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":149,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":2,"right":151,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":151,"left":3,"right":150,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":154,"right":8,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":154,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":173,"right":182,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"}